Link Aura — Your Ultimate Bio Link Builder
Link Aura is a sleek, easy-to-use web app that lets anyone create a beautiful, personalized landing page to showcase all their important links in one place — perfect for Instagram bios, TikTok profiles, or any social media.

Key Features:
Multi-user system: Each user gets their own custom, shareable link page (yourdomain.com/username)

Simple signup & login: Email/password and Google authentication

Easy link management: Add, edit, reorder, and remove links anytime

Profile customization: Upload avatar, add bio, choose background colors

Mobile-first & stunning design: Clean, modern UI with a light, airy color palette that looks amazing on any device

Instant live preview: See how your page looks while editing

Ready to monetize: Built as a scalable SaaS to sell subscription plans and premium features

Why Choose Link Aura?
Perfect for influencers, creators, freelancers, and businesses who want to drive traffic effortlessly

No coding needed — intuitive interface built for everyone

Fast, reliable, and easy to deploy on your own domain

Designed with clean code and best UX/UI practices to maximize user engagement
